import { reactive, ref } from "vue";
import { Form, useForm } from "vee-validate";

import 
{
  ReferenceNumberDropDown,
  TransactionNumbersDropDown,
  VoucherNumberDropDown,
  OkButton,
  BackButton,
  GenericDropDown
}
from "@teresol/ui-components";

export default {
  name: "MegaSet12",
  components: {
     Form,
    ReferenceNumberDropDown,
    TransactionNumbersDropDown,
    VoucherNumberDropDown,
    OkButton,
    BackButton,
    GenericDropDown
  },
  props: {
    //Add configuration object details
    configObj: {},
  },
  setup(props, { emit }) {
    useForm();
    function onSubmit(values) {
      emit("onSubmit", values);
    }

    const configObject = reactive({
      title: props.configObj,
      reference_nos_label: props.configObj.componentProps.ReferenceNosLabel,
      voucher_nos_label: props.configObj.componentProps.VoucherNosLabel,
      InformationLabel: props.configObj.componentProps.InformationLabel,
      voucherInfoLabel: props.configObj.componentProps.voucherInfoLabel,
      TransactionInfoLable: props.configObj.componentProps.TransactionInfoLable,
      transaction_numbers_label: props.configObj.componentProps.TransactionNumbersLabel,
      LabelsGroup: props.configObj.componentProps.LabelsGroup
      ? props.configObj.componentProps.LabelsGroup
      : props.configObj.componentProps,
      ReferenceNumberDropDown: props.configObj.componentProps.ReferenceNumberDropDown,
      TransactionNumbersDropDown: props.configObj.componentProps.TransactionNumbersDropDown,
      TransactionNumbersDropDown1: props.configObj.componentProps.TransactionNumbersDropDown1
      ? props.configObj.componentProps.TransactionNumbersDropDown1
      : props.configObj.componentProps,
      VoucherNumberDropDown: props.configObj.componentProps.VoucherNumberDropDown,
      OkButton: props.configObj.componentProps.OkButton,
      BackButton: props.configObj.componentProps.BackButton,
      AdvicesNumberDropDown: props.configObj.componentProps.AdvicesNumberDropDown
      ? props.configObj.componentProps.AdvicesNumberDropDown
      : props.configObj.componentProps,
      AdvicesNumberDropDown1: props.configObj.componentProps.AdvicesNumberDropDown1
      ? props.configObj.componentProps.AdvicesNumberDropDown1
      : props.configObj.componentProps,
      Section1: props.configObj.componentProps.section1,
      Section2: props.configObj.componentProps.section2,
      Section3: props.configObj.componentProps.section3
      ? props.configObj.componentProps.section3
      : props.configObj.componentProps,
    });

    return {
      onSubmit,
        configObject,
      ReferenceNumberDropDown: {
        inputSpan: ref(12), // this property to be set on screen level
        spanLabel: ref(12), // this property to be set on screen level
       
      },
      TransactionNumbersDropDown:{
        inputSpan: ref(12), // this property to be set on screen level
        spanLabel: ref(12), // this property to be set on screen level
      },
      TransactionNumbersDropDown1:{
        inputSpan: ref(13), // this property to be set on screen level
        spanLabel: ref(10), // this property to be set on screen level
      },
      VoucherNumberDropDown: {
        inputSpan: ref(12), // this property to be set on screen level
        spanLabel: ref(12), // this property to be set on screen level
      },
      AdvicesNumberDropDown: {
        inputSpan: ref(12), // this property to be set on screen level
        spanLabel: ref(12), // this property to be set on screen level
      },
      AdvicesNumberDropDown1: {
        inputSpan: ref(14), // this property to be set on screen level
        spanLabel: ref(10), // this property to be set on screen level
      },
      OkButton:{
        inputSpan: ref(24),
        nativeType:'submit', // this property to be set on screen level
      },
      BackButton:{
        nativeType:'button', // this property to be set on screen level
        inputSpan: ref(24),  // this property to be set on screen level

      },
    };
  },
};
</script>
